irl, girl, don't trip Girl, girl, girl, don't trip Girl I'm waiting for the next moment, don't blip I like to hit",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 27.18000030517578,
      "text": "I'm thinking, I'll make you mine, yeah Hey girl, don't trip, I'm thinking, I'll make",
